{"tid":1596544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：獨立調查委員會是一個方法調查        「獨立」監警會也是一個方法   強調監警會會很小心睇8.31太子站事件","createTime":"2019-09-26T14:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T03:32:11.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbd1982e36330a5cc68173c3bf6a5090e5c64d2","tid":1596544,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"【1925】林鄭指聽到市民意見很感動，強調法治是香港基石，但全部問題都冇正面直接回答。獨立調查委員會是一個方法調查，「獨立」監警會也是一個方法，強調監警會會很小心睇8.31太子站事件等。林鄭又指警方受到很大壓力，任何人違法，包括市民或公務人員，都會一視同仁。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"44fb2b05471d73f33385e409cf918e7ae15c5b19","tid":1596544,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"兩個都係獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa90bb024e45db253c49c5938e78ec7dca3c8142","tid":1596544,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:17:19.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先釋放義士<br />\n解散重組警隊 依法嚴懲黑警<br />\n即時進行雙真普選<br />\n由民選政府組織獨立調查委員會徹查</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果由777政府組織獨立調查委員會<br />\n即係自已人查自已人 有咩用！"},{"pid":"fb8d59cd1192e1628dc4e8c45fd72797f908fe16","tid":1596544,"uid":286705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"看看看而已"},{"pid":"f5685b391b1f83bd6eda92a6bb3d00511a4d6dbd","tid":1596544,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:18:22.000Z","msg":"721   811    831"},{"pid":"2669c0ad177ec284da4606dfe2980ab193c566f6","tid":1596544,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb8d59cd1192e1628dc4e8c45fd72797f908fe16","tid":1596544,"uid":286705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"看看看而已"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"小心避開敏感位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cbdc7d4d4cf15e542d835